{"tid":1102581,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【迪士尼開台】「鷹眼」獨立開劇 謝洛美維納回歸","createTime":"2019-04-11T21:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T07:46:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":30,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d47931b79b7defa0153eacca3e7c1bc09a5cac74","tid":1102581,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T21:28:43.000Z","msg":"迪士尼自從旗下Marvel影業賺大錢後動作多多，更將會推出自家串流頻道Disney+，實行將劇集都收歸自家製作，與業界龍頭Netflix一較高下。最近就有傳由謝洛美維納（Jeremy Renner）飾演的「鷹眼」一角亦會開獨立劇，故事主要講述鷹眼與繼任人Kate Bishop的故事，而主角仍然會由謝洛美維納擔正。除了鷹眼，之前已有指寒冬戰士、鷹隼、洛基、紅女巫等角色均會獨立開劇，每部劇約有6至8集，製作費亦相當龐大，並且會由Marvel主席奇雲費治（Kevin Feige）親自監製，質素有一定保證，屆時必會引來熱話。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190411/large/1554975544_47a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190411%2Flarge%2F1554975544_47a0.jpg&h=be2987e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190411/59476593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190411%2F59476593&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctznwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=a660ac64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190411%2F59476593&h=dd0c808b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190411/59476593</a>"},{"pid":"d798faa317f087ca5ab61eb54efc130e678260d3","tid":1102581,"uid":108258,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T22:03:53.000Z","msg":"對佢搵啲超英拍劇無興趣 獅子王上左之後 可唔可以考慮下拍彭彭丁滿歷險記<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/04/12/Wsj9Tw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F04%2F12%2FWsj9Tw.jpg&h=c39c4c42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c41f009c04ed1ac278c4df5eba6762d6a5856918","tid":1102581,"uid":31637,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"r